docs.summary:
The wix-members-frontend module contains functionality
for working with your site members from frontend page code.
description: The frontend Wix Members API allows you to manage member access to your site
as well as view and manage the currently logged-in member.
To use the frontend Wix Members API,
import the applicable named exports from `wix-members-frontend`:

docs.summary: The Authentication API contains functionality for authenticating members from frontend code.
description: To use the Authentication API, import `{authentication}` from the `wix-members-frontend` module:
